<P>Yes, there is to be a +PvP Only server throughout Phase IV. It will be used to focus on testing/playing in a +PvP environment (duh!) and to judge the economic success of a purely +PvP server.

<P>Your extrapolations of ideas from other games are not valid in EverQuest. I appreciate your being anxious, but please experience it first before you start stating what will or won't happen.
<P>It is different than you are imagining it.
<P>Let us shape it into something new and grand...not just a new version of the same old thing....
<P>Zariin
